The paper deals with emotion recognition using multiple modalities, including speech, text, and video. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper proposes an attention mechanism to combine the information from different modalities, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SD).
